      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·齊風·001.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">雞鳴.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>雞既鳴矣，朝既盈矣。匪雞則鳴，蒼蠅之聲。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The cock has crowed;
The court is full •
But it was not the cock that was crowing;
It was the sound of the blue flies.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
