      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·齊風·001.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">雞鳴.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>東方明矣，朝既昌矣。匪東方則明，月出之光。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The east is bright;
The court is crowded
But it was not the east that was bright; —
It was the light of the moon coming forth.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
