      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·齊風·001.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">雞鳴.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>蟲飛薨薨，甘與子同夢。會且歸矣，無庶予子憎！</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The insects are flying in buzzing crowds;
It would be sweet to lie by you and dream,
Let them not hate both me and you</seg>
      </tuv>
